This is the MATLAB code for the paper "Recognising Spontaneous Facial Micro-expressions" in ICCV'11.
If you use this code or the associated SMIC corpus please cite

@inproceedings{pfister2011micro,
  title={Recognising Spontaneous Facial Micro-expressions},
  author={Tomas Pfister and Xiaobai Li and Guoying Zhao and Matti Pietik\"ainen},
  booktitle={Proceedings of the International Conference on Computer Vision (ICCV)},
  year={2011}
}

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

-- Eye Detector --
The Haar eye detector is available on-line at http://mozart.dis.ulpgc.es/Gias/modesto_eng.html

-- Temporal Interpolation Model (TIM) --
We provide the binary code for this. For further details see
Z. Zhou, G. Zhao, and M. Pietikainen. Towards a Practical Lipreading System. In CVPR, 2011.


